chip_name: On The Border Cafe Style Tortilla
description: Join us in honoring loved ones who have passed on, celebrating Dia de los Muertos. Our crispy tortillas are a delightful tribute to the vibrant flavors and traditions of this cherished Mexican holiday.

chip_name: Estrella Garden Dill Single Lithuania Pantry
description: Celebrate Lithuania's journey to independence in 1918 from Germany and Soviet Russia. Our crisp, zesty dill chips capture the spirit of freedom with a fresh, traditional flavor.
Born on this day in 1872, President Calvin Coolidge was known for his concise speeches and direct nature. Just like him, these Wasabi-flavored chips pack a punch of flavor with each bite.
